# Sales Forecasting & Business Analytics Web Application

## Overview

This project is a web-based sales analytics application developed to help businesses analyze historical sales performance and forecast future sales trends. The application provides interactive dashboards, business insights, and forecasting capabilities to support data-driven decision-making.

## Features

* Sales Performance Dashboard
* Revenue Analysis
* Product-wise Sales Analysis
* Region-wise Sales Analysis
* Monthly Sales Trends
* Sales Forecasting
* Business Insights Generation

## Technologies Used

* Python
* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* Excel

## Business Benefits

* Improved visibility into sales performance
* Faster reporting and analysis
* Data-driven business planning
* Identification of sales trends and growth opportunities

## Project Outcome

Analyzed over 1,500+ sales records and automated sales reporting processes, reducing manual analysis effort by approximately 35%.
